For those that doesn't understand what AJ just did. The Yoruba culture demands that a young man should prostates to an elder person (parents and kings inclusive) as a sign of respect, while ladies knee instead. AJ's mom is a Yoruba & his dad is partly Yoruba. His middle names 'Olufemi' and 'Olaseni' are Yoruba names.
And for the fanatics and idiots speaking against this noble gesture, try learn about other people's culture. In Yoruba land, prostration isn't a worship but a respect! Yorubas are the 'Omoluabis'.
